

For Windows OS.

a. Setup:
   1. Download Kafka from https://kafka.apache.org/downloads.
   2. Unzip the download to C:/kafka.


b. Bring up environment:
   1. cd <Kafka install directory>/bin/windows 
   2. ./zookeeper-server-start.bat ../../config/zookeeper.properties
   3. ./kafka-server-start.bat ../../config/server.properties
   4. ./kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --partitions 2 --replication-factor 1 --topic publishReminder
   5. ./kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --partitions 2 --replication-factor 1 --topic vaccineInventory
   6. ./kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --partitions 2 --replication-factor 1 --topic shotAdministrated


   7. Bring up Mysql.


   8. 
